      • listLocations

        public Set<? extends AssignableLocation> listLocations()
        Description copied from interface: JCloudsComputeClient
        Returns all locations known to jclouds.

        Includes all locations returned by ComputeService.listAssignableLocations(). Those locations will be flagged by AssignableLocation.isAssignable().

        In addition, it also includes all Location.getParent() locations.

        Specified by:
        listLocations in interface JCloudsComputeClient
        Returns:
        all assignable locations known to jclouds
